{"tid":48193,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"點解青政晤直接申請破産去打官司, 而係叫人籌錢射落海","createTime":"2016-12-21T02:06:02.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T15:40:19.000Z","uid":57471,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"02056daee0a3476f8bb33631b719eec3c159a44b","tid":48193,"uid":57471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T02:06:03.000Z","msg":"1.  明知輸硬為何仲叫支持者籌錢, 益19政府<br />\n<br />\n2. 籌既錢先得 一半都無 有什麼用, 最後都要申請破産 把籌既錢射落海"},{"pid":"859d6297b05471c4d66278cada7dd85cece0ead6","tid":48193,"uid":18320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T02:06:33.000Z","msg":"屌你老母留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0b4962f86f6e0b561c3d95ecad53795d65bba5b","tid":48193,"uid":40469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T02:16:39.000Z","msg":"籌到錢，先過一過佢地個戶口<br />\n濕一濕下腳<br />\n然後隔一段時間再去打官司<br />\n期間會有啲事發生"},{"pid":"3d82c6da1ff5a0d114eebc4485831aa8138e42f9","tid":48193,"uid":63075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T02:20:45.000Z","msg":"籌到既錢唔會拎晒去打官司，申請破產果時還咁d，破產之後就唔洗還得咁辛苦<br />\n唔好以為破產唔洗還"},{"pid":"c5c8b474ed59d7d0b3ed927c099f301eb50aa452","tid":48193,"uid":57471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T02:22:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>籌到錢，先過一過佢地個戶口<br />\n濕一濕下腳<br />\n然後隔一段時間再去打官司<br />\n期間會有啲事發生</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問題係 最後d 錢都係 益能左19政府 <br />\n<br />\n申請破産 最少 d支持支 不用成本 去 支持你"},{"pid":"af878e8447549081cb2853cd71dc15dd5f34d1e8","tid":48193,"uid":57471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T02:25:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>籌到既錢唔會拎晒去打官司，申請破產果時還咁d，破產之後就唔洗還得咁辛苦<br />\n唔好以為破產唔洗還</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n官司 最少500 - 2000萬  (包埋終審)<br />\n立法會 最少 186萬<br />\n<br />\n還 條  能咩"},{"pid":"2047d540d5dc1669213920f4673060fbab7836dc","tid":48193,"uid":42178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T02:25:46.000Z","msg":"破左產一定冇得做議員<br />\n未破都可以發下夢有得做返<br />\n好似係"},{"pid":"efd8ea17e3059af957c068494bbae5d5fef6ce94","tid":48193,"uid":67098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T02:30:56.000Z","msg":"破產之後唔批法援咁點?"},{"pid":"00aac1668f327f1e791b9e66e9cf52939c94f58a","tid":48193,"uid":57471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T02:41:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>破產之後唔批法援咁點?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n法援 合符 資格 已經可以 申請 <br />\n<br />\n唔批 就係政治 打壓 不合程序公義  反正都係輸 起碼有 光環<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現在拉埋d 支持者落水  最後都係輸 但 輸埋d支持者出去"},{"pid":"df9f59df774226da09b04b7343ceb9738f3c9e31","tid":48193,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:07:43.000Z","msg":"而家係上訴一。定要擺保證金晌法庭先可以上訴喎, 唔籌錢俾拎保證金出嚟?"},{"pid":"f715de5e849f53bacfd3f1d7ba495ba9f1c2080b","tid":48193,"uid":40469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:21:32.000Z","msg":"青政在十月份城市論壇做嘉賓時<br />\n佢講過打官司，一定會羸<br />\n現在，連打兩場都輸<br />\n依家仲叫人籌錢<br />\n輸咗兩埸，佢都要繼續打<br />\n點解佢唔用自己錢去打官司？<br />\n唔係一定贏嗎？"},{"pid":"4c9701ec325aff224c0c0f607d5e837cabfaa7c9","tid":48193,"uid":37126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:31:18.000Z","msg":"點都好，夾錢比青政打官司<br />\n有如被騙感覺<br />\n佢地又唔按規定日期回水比政府<br />\n<br />\n夾咗錢比佢<br />\n就算比佢打贏咗<br />\n佢一定唔會回水比翻我地<br />\n<br />\n冇必要夾錢比佢地打官司<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87eaf7fb80a9666a619410ca353e4285a5ee164a","tid":48193,"uid":37253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:52:25.000Z","msg":"係呀！記得十月份城市論壇<br />\n佢做嘉賓訪問時<br />\n個樣真係洋洋得意！<br />\n<br />\n佢咁有把握打官司<br />\n佢應該會有錢去做<br />\n無論輸贏，佢都唔會破產！"},{"pid":"eed7a13abdd18af829e7289d8adb3f5e3c1eda58","tid":48193,"u